<g id="10">Step 4:</g> Capture multi-year data for trend analysis
<g id="11">Step 5:</g> Document definitions and calculation methodologies</source><seg-source><g id="7">Step 1:</g> Identify relevant worksheets/sections (e.g., &quot;Climate Action&quot;)
