<g id="13">Step 2:</g> Extract financed emissions by asset class (if available)
<g id="14">Step 3:</g> Identify insurance-associated emissions (for insurers)
<g id="15">Step 4:</g> Capture facilitated emissions (for banks/underwriters)
<g id="16">Step 5:</g> Note data quality scores and coverage percentages</source><seg-source><g id="12">Step 1:</g> Identify investment/portfolio emissions (Scope 3 Category 15)
